      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"hard-earned gold\" and \"treasure\"... lol sounds a bit dramatic. but i get the point. so if i'm paying into this, what's the actual process for getting it out at the end? like how does the agent decide when the 'conditions' are actually met?",
